Crafted by the [[Gree (species)/Legends|Gree]] [[Varat'k]] and on the [[Transport/Legends|transport]] ship [[Rokak'k Baran]], the '''Varat'k Snarap''' was not a [[Blaster/Legends|blaster]] weapon, but rather manipulated gravity to fire raking force field blasts that could vaporize another [[Starship/Legends|starship]].<ref name="The Gree Enclave">{{JournalCite|8|The Gree Enclave}}</ref>

